Tom: I went to a farm last weekend.
Anna: That sounds fun! What did you see?
Tom: I saw cows, pigs, and chickens.
Anna: Did you feed the animals?
Tom: Yes, I fed the chickens.
Anna: What did the cows do?
Tom: They ate grass all day.
Anna: Did you ride a horse?
Tom: Yes, I rode a brown horse.
Anna: I want to visit a farm, too!
